text: <../images/tbar.gif>þæt land sy unforworht into þære halgan stowe.
Si hyt ælces þinges freoh buton ferdfore & walgeweorce & brycgeweorce.
Sancta Maria & sanctæ Michahel cum sancto Petro & eallum Godes halgum gemildsige þis healdendum.
Gif hwa butan gewyrhtum hit abrecan wylle hæbbe he wið God gemæne on þam ytemestan þisses lifes buton he hit ær gebete.
